				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\chi ^2$$\end{document}χ2. The uncertainty is the sum in quadrature of the uncertainty on the position in time of the vertexes of the two fitting Gaussians; the \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
